[SN]TITLE[SN]
Fire at Blaenavon's Gilchrist Thomas Industrial Estate

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Fire crews are tackling a fire at a food processing unit in Torfaen.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Firefighters were called to the blaze at Gilchrist Thomas Industrial Estate in Blaenavon at about 03:55 BST on Sunday.
Six fire engines, two water bowsers and a hydraulic platform to tackle the blaze from above are at the scene.
Firefighters have had to withdraw from the building after part of the roof collapsed.
